msCode\">\r\n              <span class=\"label-icon\">üî¢</span>\r\n              È™åËØÅÁ†ÅÔºö\r\n            </label>\r\n            <div class=\"sms-code-wrapper\">\r\n              <div class=\"sms-code-input\">\r\n                <input\r\n                    type=\"text\"\r\n                    id=\"smsCode\"\r\n                    v-model=\"form.smsCode\"\r\n                    placeholder=\"ËØ∑ËæìÂÖ•6‰ΩçÈ™åËØÅÁ†Å\"\r\n                    class=\"form-input\"\r\n                    maxlength=\"6\"\r\n                />\r\n                <div class=\"input-decoration\">\r\n                  <div class=\"input-line\"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <button\r\n                  @click=\"sendSmsCode\"\r\n                  :disabled=\"!canSend || countdown > 0\"\r\n                  class=\"send-code-btn\"\r\n                  :class=\"{ 'disabled-btn': !canSend || countdown > 0 }\"\r\n              >\r\n                <span v-if=\"countdown > 0\">{{ countdown }}sÂêéÈáçÂèë</span>\r\n                <span v-else>ÂèëÈÄÅÈ™åËØÅÁ†Å</span>\r\n              </button>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div v-if=\"errors.smsCode\" class=\"error-message\">\r\n              {{ errors.smsCode }}\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div v-if=\"smsStatus\" class=\"sms-status\" :class=\"{ 'success': smsStatus.success, 'error': !smsStatus.success }\">\r\n              {{ smsStatus.message }}\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <button\r\n              @click=\"handleRetrievePassword\"\r\n              :disabled=\"!isFormValid || isSubmitting\"\r\n              class=\"reset-button\"\r\n              :class=\"{ 'button-disabled': !isFormValid || isSubmitting }\"\r\n          >\r\n            <span class=\"button-icon\">üîç</span>\r\n            <span class=\"button-text\">{{ isSubmitting ? 'Ê≠£Âú®Êü•ËØ¢...' : 'ÊâæÂõûÂØÜÁ†Å' }}</span>\r\n          </button>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <!-- ÂØ